::Prowl/Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Prowl nods, following Iron Raptor over the wreckage. His eyes scanned 
the ground, looking for anything of significance. He frowns.

"There's a bot trapped under there," he says, pointing down, "I'm not 
sure what condition he's in, though."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Reptilica's sparkbeat speeds up in excitement as Desmonus leans toward 
him, Bloodystrike getting closer to the femm from the other side. 
Reptilica turns a corner, tugging Desmonus along.

"You know, I have a good room we can relax in... Its not too far from 
here."
